              "type": "text",
              "text": {
                "content": "I invite you into this room to define the \"Pause\" before AGI fully hijacks the human narrative. If AI is a flood of light-speed computation, then the Lux (illumination) in this room is intentionally dimmed. We are not here for answers; we are here to observe the impulse that ",
